Class Square

    • mil.emp3.api.abstracts.Container

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IContainer, IFeature, org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoAltitudeMode, org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoBase, org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoContainer, org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoPositionGroup, org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoRenderable, org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoSquare

    public class Square
extends mil.emp3.api.abstracts.Feature
implements org.cmapi.primitives.IGeoSquare
    This class implements the EMP square feature. It accepts one (1) geographic coordinate that places the center of the square. The square's length of all sides is set with the setWidth method. And the square is centered at the coordinate.
